====
Mustard Sauce for Pulled Pork

1 ½ Cup---- Cider Vinegar

1 Cup-------Yellow Mustard

½ Cup-------Ketchup

1/3 Cup-----Packed Brown Sugar

2 Cloves----Mashed Garlic

1 Tsp--------Kosher Salt

1 Tsp--------Cayenne

½ Tsp -------Fresh Ground Pepper (I use regular ground pepper)

 

Heat for approximately 5 minutes and whisk until sugar and salt dissolve. Cool and refrigerate.
